"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-golf-1931235-Rory-McIlroy-Olympics-Paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rory McIlroywas taken aback by the level of support he received during the first round of theOlympicgolf tournament in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\", \"score\": 0.9962928255162018, \"rank\": 0.003720968390731887, \"text\": \"Rory\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Gilmore\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999936487711, \"rank\": 6.351182834257696e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old, who is competing for Ireland, finished his opening round in joint-14th position after carding a score of three-under-par.McIlroy was grouped with Scottie Scheffler and Ludvig Aberg on day one of the tournament, with fans taking a huge interest in following them around the course.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998444549547141, \"rank\": 0.0001471247413073009, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was estimated that around 25,000 people were in attendance at Le Golf National with the impressive turnout leaving McIlroy stunned.Asked what he was expecting from the fans before starting his round, he issued a short but sweet reply as he said: \\\"Not this!\\\"\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Explaining why he was so surprised, McIlroy added: \\\"With so many events going on spread all across the city, for people to venture out here and to watch us play, it was a really cool atmosphere to play in.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the weekend might get a few more people.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the first couple of days might be a little quiet but it was awesome.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"McIlroy is making his second appearance at the Olympics, having also represented Ireland in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998444549547141, \"rank\": 0.0001471247413073009, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9976499949383942, \"rank\": 0.0019712301573855504, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He narrowly missed out on the bronze medal, with Xander Schauffele taking gold ahead of Rory Sabbatini and Pan Cheng-Tsung.Comparing his two Olympic experiences, he said: \\\"Tokyo was a ghost town.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xander Schauffele\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\"}, {\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory Sabbatini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Sabbatini\"}, {\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9976499949383942, \"rank\": 0.0019712301573855504, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, this was much better.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, I think the crowd support that we all got out there was amazing.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Olympic athletes miss out on salary but medals can be worth their weight in gold  Do not miss:Transgender boxer wants Imane Khelif banned from Olympics as gender row explodes  Do not miss:Meet Team GB star Heather Watson's boyfriend who scored in Conference League  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"score\": 0.9999998652479098, \"rank\": 1.3475214171594252e-07, \"text\": \"Transgender\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \