pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was okay, it's a solid start,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A bit up and down to be expected.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not do a whole lot between The Open and here.\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some good, some not so good.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A solid opening round, a little disappointing with the three-putt at the last, but overall, as I said, a solid start and something to build on.\\\"\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3203, \"end\": 3216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.576986478356926e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3252, \"end\": 3265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.576986478356926e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"